headline: TP ranks second on Everest Group's Business Process Services Top 50™ 2025 list
summary: Global digital services leader TP, announced today that Everest Group ranked TP #2 in the BPS Top 50™ 2025 list, climbing one spot from the previous year. This global ranking from Everest Group ranks the largest third-party providers based on Business Process Services (BPS) revenues and Year-on-Year (YoY) growth.
